= Architectural Parameters

<%-
  params = manual_version.extensions.map{ |e| e.params }.flatten.sort_by!(&:name)
-%>

The following <%= params.size %> parameters are defined in this manual:

|===
| Name | Type | Existence | Description

<%- params.each do |param| -%>
| <%= param.name %>
<%-   if param.schema_known? -%>
| <%= param.schema.to_pretty_s %>
<%-   else -%>
<%-     param.schemas.each do |cond_schema| -%>
<%-       next unless cond_schema.cond.could_be_satisfied_by_cfg_arch?(cfg_arch) -%>
a| <%= cond_schema.schema.to_pretty_s %> when <%= cond_schema.cond.to_asciidoc %>
<%-     end -%>
<%-   end -%>
a| <%= param.defined_by_condition.to_asciidoc -%>
a| <%= param.description %>
<%- end -%>
|===
